WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:08.433
Let's talk about the numbers directly, because vague pricing erodes trust faster than a high number ever will.

2
00:00:10.233 --> 00:00:22.600
Wellness Kitchens run 8,400 to 10,800 rupees per square foot, depending on finish. Wardrobes start at 7,320 per square foot.

3
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:29.600
A typical 10 by 10 kitchen lands between 12 and 15 lakhs.

4
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:44.400
Payment terms: 50% advance, 40% before dispatch, 10% after installation. The process, from final order to installation, typically takes 3 to 4 months.

5
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:58.900
One flag: EMI and payment plan options are still being finalized with the finance team. Don't present that as settled — if a customer asks, tell them you'll check and follow up.

6
00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:03.733
Real numbers, shared directly.

